These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: nectarine, pear
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, tulip
1. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
2. the person who growstulip is not the person eating pear##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pear   | nectarine  |
| Sport   | rose | tulip |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: apple, lemon
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, lawyer
1. the project-manager is on the left of the lawyer##1
2. the project-manager is not the person eating lemon##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | apple | lemon      |
| Pet    | project-manager  | lawyer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
2 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, sailing
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is not the owner of the lizard##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | ferret  | lizard    |
| Sport   | handball | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, gospel
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster
1. the fan gospel is not the owner of the goldfish##6
2. the fan gospel is somewhere to the right of the fan soul##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | soul  | gospel |
| Pet    | goldfish | hamster    |

